Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.68,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\fad(489,0)}{\blur3}この想いを　消してしまうには
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.68,OP01 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Kono omoi wo keshiteshimau niwa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.59,OP01 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}To just erase these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.59,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\pos(644,652)}まだ人生長いでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.68,OP01 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mada jinsei nagai desho?
