Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.34,OP01 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is reminding me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.34,OP01 Kana,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}懐かしくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.34,OP01 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Natsukashiku naru
